{"tid":661944,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【解剖鯊魚】被素食者質疑玩弄屍體　網民：即係醫生解剖都有問題","createTime":"2018-05-12T04:09:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-12T04:35:33.000Z","uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"baee41138904e18800c4ebcc04e6c0216cd0c5db","tid":661944,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T04:09:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1432767/org/a6d8b1898a71a046739fdedb45507653.jpg/OAuEgi_ov9xtNP2_-oU_pnLhCrO7qWL-Sx1uNEsdbjQ?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1432767%2Forg%2Fa6d8b1898a71a046739fdedb45507653.jpg%2FOAuEgi_ov9xtNP2_-oU_pnLhCrO7qWL-Sx1uNEsdbjQ%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=ada9ff45&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n早前一間教育中心提供的科學課程中，有「解剖小鯊魚」的課程內容，今早卻被一名網民在素食群組中轉載有關的貼文「公審」，認為學生在課程中是「玩弄屍體」。教育中心發言人對01記者解釋，那條小鯊魚在街市買來時已死，而且是課程的內容是回應校本科學課「生態環境」的內容。<br />\n<br />\n今早有網友在facebook素食群組「素食青年」轉載有關教育中心的貼文，並指：「看看這所講教育機構在幹什麼」，即引來網民熱烈討論，有人回應指「中學生物科已經要解剖，除非唔畀小朋友讀理科」，亦有人指「咁啲醫生去解剖係唔係有問題？」<br />\n記者向該教育中心查詢，發言人Janet指，解剖魚類是回應小學6年級科學有關「生環環境」的課程，「條鯊魚係死嘅，係導師喺元朗的街市買返嚟，如果解剖一條可以喺街市買到嘅魚都有問題，我真係無語」。她又指，其實不擔心被人「公審」，但學生的樣子被放上網上群組，是最令她反感。<br />\n她又表示，很多人會嫌魚類又腥又骯髒，會不想接觸，但如讓小朋友從小接觸不同的事物，將來在中學或參與其他課程時再次遇到的話，「例如中學要劏牛眼」，他們會更有信心、更投入去學習。<br />\n除了回應校本課程的科學實驗外，教育中心另有提供3歲至14歲恆常的科學課程、季節性的日營課程和暑期課程等等，也鼓勵小朋友動手嘗試和體驗。「喺復活節舉辦咗一個有關雞蛋嘅Day camp，踩上雞蛋係學習力學，仲有其他內容係學分解雞蛋、DNA等等。」Janet說，中心會提供足夠的保護設施予學生，例如眼罩、口罩和手套等。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1432763/org/4379a7a000913bde3c0f2fe73f6709d4.png/AJ5nGgyxVsHwl8vUYBWZOuom8jSjWCwv4xrDd-Maw3c?v=w1440\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1432763%2Forg%2F4379a7a000913bde3c0f2fe73f6709d4.png%2FAJ5nGgyxVsHwl8vUYBWZOuom8jSjWCwv4xrDd-Maw3c%3Fv%3Dw1440&h=fd4027de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/親子/186948/解剖鯊魚-被素食者質疑玩弄屍體-網民-即係醫生解剖都有問題?utm_medium=Social&amp;utm_source=fbpost_link&amp;utm_campaign=parenting\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E8%A6%AA%E5%AD%90%2F186948%2F%E8%A7%A3%E5%89%96%E9%AF%8A%E9%AD%9A-%E8%A2%AB%E7%B4%A0%E9%A3%9F%E8%80%85%E8%B3%AA%E7%96%91%E7%8E%A9%E5%BC%84%E5%B1%8D%E9%AB%94-%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91-%E5%8D%B3%E4%BF%82%E9%86%AB%E7%94%9F%E8%A7%A3%E5%89%96%E9%83%BD%E6%9C%89%E5%95%8F%E9%A1%8C%3Futm_medium%3DSocial%26utm_source%3Dfbpost_link%26utm_campaign%3Dparenting&d=3juTG67kHkovhAVMyh4CYp7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=70891560\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/親子/186948/解剖鯊魚-被素食者質疑玩弄屍體-網民-即係醫生解剖都有問題?utm_medium=Social&amp;utm_source=fbpost_link&amp;utm_campaign=parenting</a>"},{"pid":"99fd7accacbcf2bd28b92b82214762b1b277b4d4","tid":661944,"uid":96871,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T04:14:02.000Z","msg":"投訴之都你估浪得虛名"},{"pid":"7e7b0a449099675e7f873187f31e79991cab6bb0","tid":661944,"uid":82532,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T04:18:17.000Z","msg":"素食撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fe5b0dbd8486d06515996afb00331ee5e691f23","tid":661944,"uid":61271,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T04:19:32.000Z","msg":"素食者打唔打飛機？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08051d8cbb000fad3c5ed03ee758d38f0432fa80","tid":661944,"uid":165978,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T04:20:38.000Z","msg":"素食撚會唔會含撚？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d01453fbf2032d64a7612e29d41bf42b78508365","tid":661944,"uid":28580,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T04:21:29.000Z","msg":"吸口氣都有微生物比你整死啦"},{"pid":"07a89a52c4227bf51d24294606f95239d0638650","tid":661944,"uid":179967,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T04:21:53.000Z","msg":"所以話係香港點解咁多人都唔敢做埋D出位既野<br />\n偏離少少都俾人擺上網公審 癡鳩線"},{"pid":"ee1c9818ad1a677264f3fc8315dac6295b005a85","tid":661944,"uid":146243,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T04:23:17.000Z","msg":"証明長期唔食肉會變智障"},{"pid":"a9fcabb6dc54960f857588fe4185c17fcdc0359b","tid":661944,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T04:23:21.000Z","msg":"素食者戇鳩d定女權撚戇鳩d"},{"pid":"d001fc3c7e4541bbb3653f2d87489d1bf48383cd","tid":661944,"uid":6222,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T04:24:45.000Z","msg":"明明就係教學用途都要屈人玩屍體<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咩心態<br />\n<br />\n同埋得罪講句 真係玩都唔覺有問題 佢已經死左 又唔係生勾勾玩死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f79df082647773695f9ada4e61eca54ddb54cbb","tid":661944,"uid":43141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T04:24:55.000Z","msg":"自己食左好耐素都覺得素撚係最on9麻煩不知所謂嘅一羣<br />\n從來唔會同佢地來往"},{"pid":"7fbb694e260e35856155fa317ff78ee996776040","tid":661944,"uid":19979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T04:26:18.000Z","msg":"好撚正wo<br />\n小學已經有解剖睇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52974e910a611a392cbd43df166a89a2bd95037b","tid":661944,"uid":15830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T04:29:32.000Z","msg":"啲素食撚真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebfca27ae9c3521d55a993341c6696283fe1a6a0","tid":661944,"uid":33477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T04:30:06.000Z","msg":"條鯊魚係死嘅，係導師喺元朗的街市買返嚟<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb45d36b7b5276d4e00d2d344d2841d2595053ce","tid":661944,"uid":8439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a9fcabb6dc54960f857588fe418